'''Nyaa Torrents'''是一个侧重于[[东亚|东亚]]（[[中国|中国]]、[[日本|日本]]及[[韩国|韩国]]）多媒体资源的[[BitTorrent_(协议)|BitTorrent]]站点。它也是世界上最大的[[动漫|动漫]]专用种子索引站。<ref name=torrentfreak1>{{cite web|url=http://torrentfreak.com/anti-piracy-outfit-denies-ddosing-anime-sites-140904/|title=Anti-Piracy Outfit Denies DDoS'ing Anime Sites | TorrentFreak|publisher=torrentfreak.com|accessdate=2014-09-05|archive-date=2014-09-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140905144505/http://torrentfreak.com/anti-piracy-outfit-denies-ddosing-anime-sites-140904/|dead-url=no}}</ref>在2011年的时候该网站一些用户就已经被列为{{link-en|版权侵害|Copyright infringement}}的目标。<ref name="torrentfreak">{{cite web|url=http://torrentfreak.com/anime-distributor-launches-piracy-assault-sues-1337-bittorrent-users-110126/|title=Anime Distributor Launches Piracy Assault, Sues 1337 BitTorrent Users | TorrentFreak|publisher=torrentfreak.com|accessdate=2014-09-05|archive-date=2014-09-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140906021048/http://torrentfreak.com/anime-distributor-launches-piracy-assault-sues-1337-bittorrent-users-110126/|dead-url=no}}</ref>在2014年该网站已被日本政府确定为主要的数字盗版网站。<ref name=torrentfreak1/>

在2014年9月上旬该网站曾遭受大规模的[[阻斷服務攻擊|DDoS]]攻击。<ref name="torrentfreak1" /><ref name="idigitaltimes">{{cite web|url=http://www.idigitaltimes.com/nyaa-anime-torrents-still-down-file-sharing-site-has-been-offline-5-days-japanese-government-isn%E2%80%99t|title=Nyaa Anime Torrents Still Down: File-Sharing Site Has Been Offline For 5 Days, But Japanese Government Isn’t Likely The Culprit|publisher=idigitaltimes.com|accessdate=2014-09-05|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140906022706/http://www.idigitaltimes.com/nyaa-anime-torrents-still-down-file-sharing-site-has-been-offline-5-days-japanese-government-isn%E2%80%99t|archivedate=2014-09-06}}</ref>

2017年5月1日，该站的[[.se|.se]]、[[.eu|.eu]]和[[.org|.org]]域名被该站或DNS管理员置为非活动状态，网站下线<ref name="Torrentfreak3">{{cite web |url=https://torrentfreak.com/anime-torrent-site-nyaa-goes-down-after-domain-name-deactivation-170502/ |title=Anime Torrent Site NYAA Goes Down After Domain Name Deactivation | TorrentFreak |publisher=torrentfreak.com |date=2017-05-02 |accessdate=2017-05-02 |language=en |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170502163626/https://torrentfreak.com/anime-torrent-site-nyaa-goes-down-after-domain-name-deactivation-170502/ |archivedate=2017-05-02 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。其后不久，德国公司Goodlabs买下.eu域名，并换成[[钓鱼网站|钓鱼网站]]引导用户下载[[恶意软件|恶意软件]]<ref name="scam">{{cite web |url=https://torrentfreak.com/scammers-pick-up-nyaa-torrents-domain-name-170624/ |title=Scammers Pick Up NYAA Torrents Domain Name |date=2017-06-24 |website={{Link-en|TorrentFreak}} |publisher= |access-date=2020-09-17 |quote=Just a few weeks after the domain names of anime torrent site NYAA were deactivated, one of them is back in action. However, the domain no longer belongs to the old crew, but to scammers who are trying to lure irreproachable users into downloading harmful content. |archive-date=2019-07-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190714224727/https://torrentfreak.com/scammers-pick-up-nyaa-torrents-domain-name-170624/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2017年5月10日，该站于[[.si|.si]]域名重新上线，并命名为NyaaV2，继承原站的全部资源。<ref name="NyaaV2Up">{{cite web|url=https://steamcn.com/forum.php?mod=viewthread&tid=270303&page=1|title=Nyaa复活了|publisher=steamcn.com|date=2017-05-11|accessdate=2018-07-23|dead-url=yes|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180723003606/https://steamcn.com/forum.php?mod=viewthread&tid=270303&page=1|archive-date=2018-07-23}}</ref>

2018年7月22日，该站.si域名遭到DDoS攻击，下线约7个小时。<ref name="NyaaV2Down"/>

